            . On the 19th of January, between eleven and twelve o'clock in the day, I was by <placeName id="t18210214-24-crimeloc157">St. Sepulchres Church</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18210214-24-crimeloc157" type="placeName" value="St. Sepulchres Church"></interp>
