                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-24-off155 t18210214-24-crimeloc157"></join>, with my sister. I felt some one touching me, turned round, and saw the prisoner with my handkerchief; I pursued, and took it from his bosom; I secured him, and told him to deliver it up; he said,</p>
               <p>"I will if you will let me go." The constable came up, and took him in charge.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
